notes.p: ARF degradation rate, based on the value for ARF1, cf. Salmon et al. The Plant Journal (2008)
Aux/IAA basal degradation rate (without auxin), based on half-lifes measured in Dreher et al. The Plant Cell 2006.
Auxin target gene mRNA degradation rate. Computed from the mean half life of Aux/IAA mRNA in Narsai et al. The Plant Cell 2007.
